Template: bozomake/purgeoldscriptinhomedir
Type: boolean
Description: Find and purge user's locally-installed versions ?
	Set wether user's bin dir must be scanned for
	collisionning scripts and rename them so that the
	whole system is coherent with this release of
	bozomake set.
	.
	As bozomake is targetting super-users, the default is to
	perform the scan.

